text: Little Fell may refer to: *Little Fell (Mallerstang) (667m), a "Hewitt" in the Yorkshire Dales, England *Little Fell (Mickle Fell) (748m), a "Hewitt" in the North Pennines, England *Little Fell (Wild Boar Fell) (559m), a subsidiary summit of Wild Boar Fell, Yorkshire Dales, England *Little Fell (Lowther Hills) (356m), a summit in the south west of the Lowther Hills, Dumfries and Galloway, Scotland
title: Little Fell
